music/watch-biffy-clyro-play-blackened-sky-in-full-along-with-rarities-as-they-kick-off-london-residency-video-setlist-3804711">观看 Biffy Clyro 在伦敦驻场演出时完整演奏《Blackened Sky》以及稀有曲目的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
