lellan 拍摄的一些照片。 </p><figure id="attachment_3804733" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804733" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804733" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB1@2000.jpg" alt="利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 由阿拉斯代尔·麦克莱伦 (Alasdair Mcclellan) 为 Berghaus 设计" width="2000" height="2463" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB1@2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB1@2000-400x493.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB1@2000-800x985.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB1@2000-324x400.jpg 324w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB1@2000-696x857.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB1@2000-1392x1714.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB1@2000-1068x1315.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3804733" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)，阿拉斯代尔·麦克莱伦 (Alasdair Mcclellan) 为 Berghaus 设计。图片来源：Alasdair Mclellan for Berghaus </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3804734" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804734" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804734" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB2@2000.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="2484" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB2@2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB2@2000-400x497.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB2@2000-800x994.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB2@2000-696x864.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LG-Berghaus-FB2@2000-1392x1729.jpg 1392